      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. Honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled right off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I've totally babied this car since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still has that fresh feel every time you get behind the wheel. It drives like an absolute dream! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
