    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example boasts a factory-correct 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a fully serviced VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains structurally flawless with verified subframe integrity. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car retains its original suspension kinematics and factory-honed damping characteristics. Mechanically impeccable with zero fluid seepage, this unit delivers the raw, analog tactile feedback and linear power delivery defining the golden era of M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
