    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, mirror-like paint finish that is entirely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. The interior is a masterclass in care; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, while the high-gloss trim and digital displays are completely scratch-free. Mechanically, it performs with the same tightness and responsiveness as the day it was delivered, supported by a folder of exhaustive service records from a certified master technician. Every button, sensor, and feature operates with factory precision. For the buyer who demands a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
